quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,119,"Thumma inna rabbaka lillatheenaAAamiloo assoo-a bijahalatin thumma taboomin baAAdi thalika waaslahoo inna rabbakamin baAAdiha laghafoorun raheem"
  16,120,"Inna ibraheema kana ommatan qanitanlillahi haneefan walam yaku mina almushrikeen"
  16,121,"Shakiran li-anAAumihi ijtabahuwahadahu ila siratin mustaqeem"
  16,122,"Waataynahu fee addunyahasanatan wa-innahu fee al-akhirati lamina assaliheen"
  16,123,"Thumma awhayna ilayka aniittabiAA millata ibraheema haneefan wama kanamina almushrikeen"
  16,124,"Innama juAAila assabtu AAalaallatheena ikhtalafoo feehi wa-inna rabbaka layahkumubaynahum yawma alqiyamati feema kanoo feehiyakhtalifoon"
  16,125,"OdAAu ila sabeeli rabbika bilhikmatiwalmawAAithati alhasanati wajadilhumbillatee hiya ahsanu inna rabbaka huwa aAAlamubiman dalla AAan sabeelihi wahuwa aAAlamu bilmuhtadeen"
  16,126,"Wa-in AAaqabtum faAAaqiboobimithli ma AAooqibtum bihi wala-in sabartum lahuwakhayrun lissabireen"
  16,127,"Wasbir wama sabrukailla billahi wala tahzanAAalayhim wala taku fee dayqin mimmayamkuroon"
  16,128,"Inna Allaha maAAa allatheenaittaqaw wallatheena hum muhsinoon"
